SubjectAgreement between Canada and the the Republic of Poland for Cooperation in the Peaceful Uses of Nuclear Energy (the “Agreement”).
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs, or a delegate, to sign, on behalf of the Governement of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT BETWEEN CANADA AND THE REPUBLIC OF POLAND FOR COOPERATION IN THE PEACEFUL USES OF NUCLEAR ENERGY.
